title: George Osborne accused of bullying peers over opposition to tax credit cuts
text: George Osborne has been accused of implementing bullying tactics to push his tax credit policy through the House of Lords . A peer leading the threats to block cuts to tax credits unless the Government eases the impact on low-paid families
